name: Harvey
description: This is Harvey!  Harvey is an average sized fluffle with common coat, ears, frill, body and tail.  Harvey is a little bit of a chunker and will need a lot of exercise to maintain a healthy weight. They are not a huge fan of any form of enrichment that doesnt involve food so you will need to use some inventiveness to get them moving.   Harveys favorite past time is crowding on the couch to watch movies, with romcoms as the clear favorite.   -Warning, do NOT turn off a romcom before it is concluded. The most energy we have ever seen from this fluffle was during a power loss that resulted in Harvey missing the ending of 50 first dates.
